content.html: Kid is running for School Board. A few weeks ago my kid was approached by a parent with a list of approx 200 books she wanted banned. My kid glanced at list & gave back saying “After you read these books, give me page # & reason for ban & I’ll look into it”. Hasn’t heard back.
